PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775758265
OL,3,CArtemis crew share stories of lifelong
OL,4,Cbonds, tears shed and fears of re-entry
OL,6,F"It was definitely a very emotional
OL,7,Fmoment. I don't think most of us knew
OL,8,Fit was coming," NASA lunar scientist
OL,9,FRyan Watkins said on Wednesday from
OL,10,FJohnson Space Center in Houston.
OL,11,F"There was not a single dry eye."
OL,13,FThe proposed Carroll Crater is at the
OL,14,Fleft limb on the boundary of the
OL,15,Fmoon's near and far sides, and
OL,16,Foccasionally visible from Earth.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@OO]sD@AOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
