PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775758265
OL,3,CArtemis crew share stories of lifelong
OL,4,Cbonds, tears shed and fears of re-entry
OL,6,FIt is rather shallow and approximately
OL,7,Fthree miles across, according to
OL,8,FWatkins. A slightly bigger crater,
OL,9,Fdubbed "Integrity", is completely on
OL,10,Fthe lunar far side.
OL,12,FTheir request came shortly after they
OL,13,Fbroke Apollo 13's distance record for
OL,14,Fdeep-space travelers. All four
OL,15,Fastronauts wept as they embraced in a
OL,16,Fgroup hug.
OL,18,FOnce back on Earth later this week,
OL,19,Fthe crew will submit the two proposed
OL,20,Fnames to the International
OL,21,FAstronomical Union.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
