PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775758265
OL,3,CArtemis crew share stories of lifelong
OL,4,Cbonds, tears shed and fears of re-entry
OL,6,FDespite the emotional moments, the
OL,7,Fcrew also remained laser-focused on
OL,8,Fthe difficult tasks ahead.
OL,10,FEven though they have travelled
OL,11,Ffurther than any other human being,
OL,12,Fthe most difficult part of their
OL,13,Fjourney is arguably still to come.
