OL,3,CArtemis crew share stories of lifelong
OL,4,Cbonds, tears shed and fears of re-entry
OL,6,FWhen asked about their fears for re-
OL,7,Fentering the atmosphere pilot Victor
OL,8,FGlover said: "I've actually been
OL,9,Fthinking about entry since April 3,
OL,10,F2023 when we got assigned to this
OL,11,Fmission and one of the first press
OL,12,Fconferences, we were asked, what are
OL,13,Fwe looking forward to?
OL,15,F"And I said, splashdown. And it's kind
OL,16,Fof humorous, but it's literal as well
OL,17,Fthat we have to get back.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
