FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775758265
OL,3,CArtemis crew share stories of lifelong
OL,4,Cbonds, tears shed and fears of re-entry
OL,6,F"There's so many more pictures, so
OL,7,Fmany more stories, and gosh, I haven't
OL,8,Feven begun to process what we've been
OL,9,Fthrough. We've still got two more
OL,10,Fdays, and riding a fireball through
OL,11,Fthe atmosphere is profound as well."
OL,13,FThe crew is due to return to Earth on
OL,14,FSaturday, around midnight UK time.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
